{
  "stem": "2578.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a while, when it was filled, one of us had to take it out and dump it someplace and again bring it back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For 18 days.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened was that, during the day, since we didn't do anything, we-- we were allowed to go outside this barrack, just standing around.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, for some reason, my brother moved over to a different barrack, as far as I can-- as far as I could tell.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, since this bar-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Since the Jews of this barrack were selected to be shipped out to work, he was among them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the evening-- and I didn't realize it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But towards evening, when we went inside the barrack to be ready to go to sleep, I noticed that he is missing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he usually-- we would try to get together towards evening, so when we go in to sleep, we should stay together.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In this case, he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I realized that, since the barrack next to this one, to ours, was selected to go out to be shipped out to work, he must have been included in this group.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 20-- he was about 18 years old, 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The following day, I was looking around for a-- area, hoping that another barrack will be chosen to be shipped out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it just happened that one of these barracks were emptied and marched over to the place where they would be shipped out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I joined this group.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took off my clothes, and they gave me these striped uniform-- dressed-- like-- you know, with the rest of others.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was shipped out to Germany, to a camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
